From: Thomas Zimmermann <tzimmermann@suse.de>
Date: Wed, 26 Feb 2025 18:03:09 +0100
Subject: drm/gem-framebuffer: Test for imported buffers with
 drm_gem_is_imported()
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 3d672f483e5dc99053b9c94bd0e5f504c2e3f758
